<br>
If the group was a pickup group without all SGA typical loot rules are that once you win a roll youre out until all others win something.<br>
<br>
Remember, these rules are only in place in case people try to abuse others over loot.  They are not there to keep loot from people, but to keep loot from tearing us apart. Everyone ive ever grouped with in the SGA has been very fair about the looting process and I would expect that from all the members.<br>
